      "description": "Budget-friendly and full of potential, this vehicle is a straightforward value option for someone seeking dependable basic transportation or a practical project. It shows its age cosmetically, but it remains an accessible way to get on the road without a major investment. A sensible choice for buyers who appreciate honest pricing and real-world utility.",
