    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly ride with plenty of life left for the right buyer. It\u2019s not a show car, but it\u2019s a great opportunity for someone who wants affordable transportation, a project, or a handy extra vehicle to have around. Priced to reflect its condition, and sold by someone who believes in being straightforward and easy to deal with. If you\u2019re looking for honest value and a car with potential, this one is worth a look.",
      "price": 7900.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid project car with a strong-running engine, responsive automatic, and straight-driving chassis. It shows cosmetic wear and needs attention in spots, but the core drivetrain feels stout and it remains a great candidate for a budget daily, weekend wrenching project, or platform to build on. Starts, runs, and moves with the kind of mechanical honesty enthusiasts appreciate. Priced to reflect condition while leaving room for the next owner to add value.",
