    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Honest, gritty, and full of old-school character, this car has the kind of presence that makes every drive feel like a story in progress. It\u2019s not pretending to be showroom fresh\u2014that\u2019s part of the appeal. What it offers is an affordable entry point for someone who appreciates a vehicle with personality, useful life still to give, and room to make it their own. Whether you want a budget-friendly runabout, a hands-on project, or just something with a little soul, this one has the kind of rugged charm that\u2019s getting harder to find.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "A straightforward, budget-friendly vehicle that offers an affordable path into ownership. This car shows its age, but it remains a practical option for a buyer seeking basic transportation, a project, or a dependable extra vehicle. Priced to reflect its condition while still delivering solid value, it\u2019s a sensible choice for anyone who appreciates an honest deal.",
      "price": 4950.0,
