    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Honest little car that\u2019s far from perfect, but it\u2019s an affordable way into motoring for someone who doesn\u2019t mind a few rough edges. It\u2019s got that dependable, no-nonsense charm and could suit a handy buyer, a budget commuter, or someone after a cheap runabout. Priced to reflect its condition, but there\u2019s still plenty of value here for the right person. Come have a look and see if it\u2019s the right fit for you.",
      "price": 5950.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Solid candidate for a budget build, shop truck, or dependable A-to-B driver. Advertised in poor condition, but it still offers strong utility with a complete drivetrain, usable cabin, and the kind of straightforward mechanical layout that makes servicing and sorting approachable. Engine starts, transmission engages, and it has the rugged, no-nonsense character enthusiasts look for when they want something they can improve over time. Not a showpiece, but a worthwhile project with honest bones and real everyday potential.",
